%F A073470 a(n) ~ exp(3^(4/3) * Pi^(1/3) * zeta(3/2)^(2/3) * n^(1/3) / 2) * zeta(3/2) / (9 * Pi * 2^(7/2) * n^(3/2)) * (1 + (9*Pi * zeta(1/2) * zeta(3/2) - 280) / (16 * 3^(7/3) * Pi^(1/3) * zeta(3/2)^(2/3) * n^(1/3))). - _Vaclav Kotesovec_, Mar 08 2026
%o A073470 (Magma) function a007294(n, k) return n gt k*(k+1)/2 select a007294(n-k*(k+1)/2, k) + a007294(n, k+1) else n eq k*(k+1)/2 select 1 else 0; end function; [ a007294(n, 1): n in [0..135 by 3] ]; // _Klaus Brockhaus_, Jan 23 2009
